metadata.title: Instinct Original Small Breed Grain Free Real Chicken Recipe Natural Wet Canned Dog Food, 3 oz. Cans (Pack of 24)
features: SMALL BREED GRAIN FREE DOG FOOD WITH CAGE FREE CHICKEN: Instinct Original is made with real cage free chicken, vegetables, fruits & other wholesome ingredients. This is high protein dog food with responsibly sourced cage free chicken as the #1 ingredient.

CANNED DOG FOOD WITH NO FILLERS: Instinct Original wet dog food is high protein dog food. Made without grain, potato, corn, wheat, soy, carrageenan, by-product meals, artificial colors or preservatives - ingredients known to trigger food sensitivities.

NATURAL DOG FOOD: Made from real meat & whole food ingredients, our grain free wet dog food is packed with animal protein for strong, lean muscles. Served as a meal or topper, this delicious loaf texture is a taste that small dogs crave.

RAW INSPIRED WET DOG FOOD FOR SMALL DOG: Our canned dog food offers complete & balanced nutrition from real ingredients to support your dog's health from puppy to senior. Made in the USA with the finest ingredients from around the world.

INSTINCT, THE RAW BRAND: We craft wet & dry dog food from real ingredients. Compare Instinct to Blue Buffalo, Rachel Ray, Hills Science Diet, Purina One, Taste of the Wild, Merrick, Natural Balance, Wellness, Orijen, Royal Canin, Fromm, Acana & Nutro.
description: High animal protein, grain-free recipe guided by our belief in raw, Instinct Original Real Chicken Recipe for Small Breed Dogs unlock your dog's potential to thrive. Made with real, natural ingredients, these grain-free recipes started with real meat and are a great option to create mealtime excitement, increase hydration and provide a high protein meal.
